summary:
Exploration geologist/geophysicist  with extensive experience in seismic interpretation and structural geology. Working mainly in Exploration teams in a multicultural environments. High score at college, graduate diplomas and master degree's. 

Specialties: Seismic Interpretation, seismo-stratigraphy, geophysics, structural geology, kinematics of deformation  and Basin Analysis.
